Zero Trust Logical Components - Quick Reference
- PDP (Policy Decision Point) = decision-making department
  - PE (Policy Engine) = evaluates and decides (judge)
  - PA (Policy Administrator) = communicates decision (messenger)
- PEP (Policy Enforcement Point) = actually allows/denies access (gatekeeper)


