Quick Reference - Power Protection
- Short + drop = Sag | Long + drop = Brownout | Zero = Blackout
- Short + rise = Spike | Long + rise = Surge

Fail-Safe vs Fail-Secure
- Fail-Safe = access allowed on failure (safety priority) - e.g. fire alarm unlocks doors
- Fail-Secure = access denied on failure (security priority) - e.g. server room stays locked


